overview: Initiation Night Now well into the first semester of her freshman year, Kelly is about to be initiated into the hottest Sorority on campus - the Pi Pi's. But first, there's that little matter of her geography class she's failing. I wonder what the professor wants to see her about? Also: Watch a hot little 18 year old freshman deaf student get analized!
title: Kelly the Coed 2 - Initiation Night
